TrBc9jhB1GxL9BITyYQOVBdb3eWOIYwiZpmeEC-vSErikWRQ\",\"summary\":[]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"No extra Maven dependency or Docker service is needed for meaningful Vert.x Web Client coverage because normal usage can be exercised against an in-process Vert.x HttpServer. However, io.vertx:vertx-web-client:5.0.1 resolves Vert.x Core 5.0.1 with Netty 4.2.2.Final, and Netty disables Unsafe by default on Java 24+ unless explicitly allowed, which matches the JDK 25 native-runtime failure context.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For native test execution on JDK 25, set runtime system properties for the generated native test binary: -Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true. Keep tests self-contained by using a loopback Vert.x HttpServer/WebClient pair and closing WebClient, HttpServer, and Vertx in finally blocks.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The Unsafe property is tied to Netty behavior on Java 24+; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\",\n    \"OAuth2WebClient scenarios may require optional vertx-auth-oauth2 setup, but ordinary WebClient, BodyCodec, multipart, caching, session, redirect, and header coverage does not.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09649d13c20e86bb016a3e8d1a52188193b2026ce6843dc64a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1824, "output": 728, "cacheRead": 36864, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 39416, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782484240536, "responseId": "resp_09649d13c20e86bb016a3e8d10fb208193b648f07aa8361e99"}, "toolResults": []}
